        "collapsible_tab_4": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "column": "under-gallery",
            "heading": "Gizmo the Grey Bird's Story & Mission",
            "heading_size": "large",
            "heading_tag": "h4",
            "icon": "none",
            "no_padding": true,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Meet_The_Flock_Behind_the_Squawk_2400_x_2400_px_1.png",
            "content": "<p>After spending over 16 years trapped in a cage with no enrichment, no toys, and no real life, Gizmo’s journey became our inspiration. His resilience reminds us how deeply parrots rely on proper stimulation, love, and freedom to thrive. That’s why Squawk Shop is dedicated to giving birds around the world access to safe, premium, and affordable enrichment—so no parrot ever has to go without the joy and quality of life they deserve.</p>",
