    "testimonials": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "column_1": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "rating": true,
            "rating_stars": "5-star",
            "text": "<p>My Blue and Gold Macaw absolutely love how big these toys are from Squawk Shop. I like to hide nuts in the rattan balls for him to go foraging.</p>",
            "title": "— Kelsey C. · Verified Buyer",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Screenshot_2025-11-20_at_3.19.25_PM.png",
            "hide_image": false,
            "product": "ball-thing-monster"
          }
        },
        "column_2": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "rating": true,
            "rating_stars": "5-star",
            "text": "<p>I’ve never seen my African Grey this happy! The Java Tree we ordered was exactly the one shown online, and the quality is unbelievable. The natural branches encourage climbing, chewing, and exploring every day. It’s stunning in our living room and has completely transformed his daily routine. Squawk Shop genuinely cares about birds, and you can feel it in every product.</p>",
            "title": "— Brenda R. · Verified Buyer",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/20251120_1525_Woman_with_Parrot_simple_compose_01kahnxkw6epmsz1dx66fydw6n.png",
            "hide_image": false,
            "product": "java-tree-4"
          }
        },
        "column_3": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "rating": true,
            "rating_stars": "5-star",
            "text": "<p>We purchased a new cage and were blown away by the quality. The free essentials bundle was such a thoughtful addition and made setup incredibly easy. Everything was packaged perfectly and arrived in pristine condition. My conure has so much more space now, and I feel confident knowing everything is bird-safe and built to last.</p>",
            "title": "— Alisha T. · Verified Buyer",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/close-up-of-parakeet-biting-finger-534563317-5b554aecc9e77c003712b1f9.jpg",
            "hide_image": false,
            "product": "majestic-series-medium-cage-bundle"
          }
        },
        "column_4": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "rating": true,
            "rating_stars": "5-star",
            "text": "<p>This cat toilet is a game-changer! It’s spacious, easy to clean, and fits perfectly in my home. My cat feels comfortable and happy using it every day. The design is sleek and modern, blending seamlessly with my decor.</p>",
            "title": "James Martin",
            "hide_image": false,
            "product": ""
          }
        },
        "column_5": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "rating": true,
            "rating_stars": "5-star",
            "text": "<p>Since switching to Mellow Dream, my cat’s calmness has noticeably improved. She’s more relaxed and sleeps better through the night. The natural ingredients really make a difference—highly recommend for any cat with anxiety!</p>",
            "title": "Sophia Johnson",
            "hide_image": false,
            "product": ""
          }
        },
        "column_6": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "rating": true,
            "rating_stars": "5-star",
            "text": "<p>The waterproof raincoat keeps my dog dry and comfortable during rainy walks. It fits perfectly and doesn’t restrict movement. Plus, it’s easy to put on and take off — highly recommend!</p>",
            "title": "Liam Wilson",
            "hide_image": false,
            "product": ""
          }
        }
      },
